@copying
This manual documents the in-tree parts of VibeOS as they exist in this
repository.

The manual covers the kernel, the in-tree userspace helper program, the image
construction pipeline, the top-level build rules, and the way VibeOS integrates
upstream packages.  It does not try to replace the manuals shipped by upstream
projects inside @file{external/}; instead, it documents the VibeOS-specific
policy, staging, and compatibility behavior around them.
@end copying

